      <title>抗议活动扰乱市场秩序 印尼部署数千名警察</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/jakarta-deploys-police-as-jokowi-prabowo-bloc-provokes-backlash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼民众对选举改革计划愈发愤怒，数千名警察被部署在议会大厦附近。选举改革计划实际上将有利于总统佐科·维多多 (Joko Widodo) 和即将上任的继任者普拉博沃·苏比安托 (Prabowo Subianto) 之间的联盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/jakarta-deploys-police-as-jokowi-prabowo-bloc-provokes-backlash</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 02:43:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>另一艘“暗黑舰队”油轮将驶往受制裁的俄罗斯液化天然气工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/another-dark-fleet-tanker-set-for-sanctioned-russian-lng-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[第三艘液化天然气运输船似乎正驶往受到美国制裁的俄罗斯北部北极液化天然气 2 号出口工厂，而莫斯科方面正在加大力度规避西方的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/another-dark-fleet-tanker-set-for-sanctioned-russian-lng-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 02:35:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西将限制部分游客入境以阻止非法移民进入美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/brazil-to-limit-some-visitors-to-stem-illegal-migration-to-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西将开始限制中国和印度等国公民入境，以打击抵达这个南美国家后试图非法移民至美国和加拿大的人员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/brazil-to-limit-some-visitors-to-stem-illegal-migration-to-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 02:28:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普华永道预计恒大集团审计业务将被禁止在中国开展六个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/pwc-china-unit-expects-six-month-ban-from-government-ft-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，普华永道中国分部预计，中国政府将因其对破产的房地产巨头中国恒大集团的审计而对其实施为期六个月的禁令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/pwc-china-unit-expects-six-month-ban-from-government-ft-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 23:11:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>蒂姆·沃尔兹带领民主党新星在大会期间针对特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/dnc-2024-tim-walz-leads-democratic-rising-stars-targeting-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党在星期三于芝加哥举行的全国代表大会上，把焦点转向下一代党内明星，试图将共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普描绘成一位年纪较大、与现实脱节的候选人和生存危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/dnc-2024-tim-walz-leads-democratic-rising-stars-targeting-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰政府希望市长们勒紧裤腰带，遏制“幻想”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/nz-government-wants-mayors-to-tighten-belts-rein-in-fantasies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰政府宣布了一项提案，鼓励地方议会对必要的基础设施进行更多投资，同时向市长们发出信息，要求他们停止不合理的支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/nz-government-wants-mayors-to-tighten-belts-rein-in-fantasies</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 21:52:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯 11 天内获得的捐款比拜登整个竞选期间获得的捐款还多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/kamala-harris-total-donors-exceed-biden-s-entire-campaign-in-just-11-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[七月份的筹款数据显示，佐治亚州和北卡罗来纳州这两个摇摆州的捐赠热情很高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/kamala-harris-total-donors-exceed-biden-s-entire-campaign-in-just-11-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 21:35:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大主要铁路濒临停运，特鲁多敦促达成协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/trudeau-calls-on-railways-union-to-reach-deal-to-stave-off-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多呼吁加拿大两大铁路公司和工会工人达成协议，避免停工，企业表示停工将对加拿大和美国经济造成重大损害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/trudeau-calls-on-railways-union-to-reach-deal-to-stave-off-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 17:24:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中美争夺支持 太平洋“大博弈”展开</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/new-great-game-unfolds-in-pacific-as-us-china-vie-for-backing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分布在太平洋上的岛国正处于中美两国为争夺海上航线、深水港和其他战略资产而展开的激烈竞争的中心，洛伊研究所称之为一场新的“大博弈”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/new-great-game-unfolds-in-pacific-as-us-china-vie-for-backing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯称加沙停火协议“时间至关重要”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/blinken-says-time-is-of-the-essence-for-gaza-cease-fire-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周二晚间离开中东，哈马斯和以色列仍然对美国提出的暂停甚至永久结束加沙战争的提议存在分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/blinken-says-time-is-of-the-essence-for-gaza-cease-fire-deal</guid>
